            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
