      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pepper strips </strong>and <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 5 min or until they've softened slightly</p>",
